Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:06.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.51,0:00:11.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:14.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:16.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:17.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:19.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:22.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:24.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It really hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:26.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:28.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:29.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:31.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:37.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened... to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:09.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:10.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:14.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:15.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:16.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:19.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:19.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:21.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:24.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's really no need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:27.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that field of pampas grass?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:28.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:28.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:36.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:38.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:43.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am holding her, but it's not what you think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:47.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I gave an innocent girl some alcohol and took her to a secluded place...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:48.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:50.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:56.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:57.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:03:00.57,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\c&HB83D41&\pos(643,96)}Episode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:03.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it enough, but I am very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:06.66,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\frx358\fry26\frz345.07\c&H3E1F00&\pos(739,379)}KIRISHIMA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:06.66,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\frx358\fry26\frz345.07\c&H3E1F00&\pos(1060,491)}CLINIC
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:06.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't aware of the situation, so I became a little upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You call that "a little upset"? You old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:11.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to apologize too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:15.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Yukito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:17.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:18.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamio,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu Kamio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:20.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face seems familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:25.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really stand out much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:27.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we've met before
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:30.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,since you've been here a few times for checkups.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:38.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, lots of weird things really did happen on your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:41.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that just makes it all the more memorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:45.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you become friends with Kano instead of just playing with me all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:47.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you might get along pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:49.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're both pretty weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:52.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:54.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:55.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to get my pay for today's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:01.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you wait till tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:05.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be difficult if I try to pick it up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's my-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:10.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:13.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've gone to sleep already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:25.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eeep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:26.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to turn the lights on so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:33.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't properly examine you in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:36.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... Kano, you've grown so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:39.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:41.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me in weird places.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:43.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a proper clinical technique called "palpation".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:46.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Examinations don't require caressing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:47.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:49.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:50.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:52.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess it was just a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:55.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't have any cats here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:56.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:57.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:00.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Kano, let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.47,0:05:02.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:03.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong, Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:07.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:10.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Repeating the same words, over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:21.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This child is my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:23.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,my only treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:23.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my precious little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:29.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What, what, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:32.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Onee-chan hugging me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:33.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were falling asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:34.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:38.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You came and hugged me, so I held you in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:38.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:40.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:43.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to hurry up and go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:44.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:47.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But can we stay like this for just a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:51.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You held me like this when Daddy passed away – remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:52.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:54.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:55.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you smell nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, a cicada flew in through the vent again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:05.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, the soy sauce bottle fell over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:08.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, the salad oil spilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:12.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, Yukito-san's bacon and eggs got messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah-wah-wah-wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:19.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:30.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, something happened to this food, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:33.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:47.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at me as if, "wow, he's actually eating it!"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:50.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not looking like that, not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san, is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:06:59.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:01.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:02.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't taste like cicadas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:06.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:13.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:14.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:15.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:17.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:18.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:19.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:20.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:21.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... this and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:26.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll see you later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:27.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:31.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:48.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least do enough to earn your wages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:54.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done everything already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:55.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I have something else for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:56.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:03.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to say something, just say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But a pay raise is out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:06.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:08.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:12.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's about last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:12.34,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:15.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, I haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:20.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've been looking for him for a while, but I can't seem to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:22.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:23.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:26.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:29.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato, come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:33.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:35.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:40.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato... Where could he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:45.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun's starting to set now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:51.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:58.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:01.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of anywhere else to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:05.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you use your magic to find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:08.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:13.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think my magic works like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:14.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:18.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was given this bandana,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:21.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to keep it on until I become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it off until then, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:26.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I take it off, I'll be able to use my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:30.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was little, so I don't remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:33.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's been wrapped around my wrist ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:38.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been troublesome at times, like during swimming and health checkups,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:40.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was even teased a few times too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:41.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:44.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know, Onee-chan always saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:47.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I've been able to make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:48.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:51.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come all the way to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:53.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he could possibly be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:57.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:01.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yukito-kun, what's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized where Potato is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:03.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:04.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:05.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:06.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:07.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:08.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:09.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:14.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:16.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:17.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:18.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:21.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:24.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, don't ever make me worry like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:25.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:28.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what were you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:31.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yukito-kun, how did you know that he was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:33.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... well... uh... what do you call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:35.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko Pikopik-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:38.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a kind of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:38.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:40.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen, Potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:46.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever wander off again without telling me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:49.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're just saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:52.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:53.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:54.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:58.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really not remember anything about what happened last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:00.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:01.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:02.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:05.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-kun, will you listen to something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:14.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, you can tell me anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:18.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hardly remember anything about my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:21.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she was never very healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:24.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She became sick right after she gave birth to me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and passed away when I was about three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:32.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad would often say, "Your mom was like you."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:35.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still couldn't picture her very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:40.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but, you know? It's not so bad; I wasn't that lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:44.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan was like a mom to me, and Dad was always around too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:58.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that means that Onee-chan was without a mom for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:01.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, I realized how unfair that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:07.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad was always busy with the clinic, and then he got sick himself from working too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:16.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I could do was watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:23.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan works and takes care of me, but I can't really do anything to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:26.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not much help either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:28.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:36.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could use magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:38.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:41.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,would use it to meet my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet her and apologize
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:45.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:54.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should thank her, not apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:55.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:58.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother is the reason that you're here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:02.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone said to me, "I'm sorry that you gave birth to me,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:15.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your mom, Yukito-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:17.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:18.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not here anymore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:22.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, she went to the same place your mom is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:24.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:28.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom was looking for a girl in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:30.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:34.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Somewhere beyond this sky is a girl with wings."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my mom's favorite saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:38.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for that girl too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:39.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:45.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, some day when I can fly, I'll look for that girl for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:52.85,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\fsp2\pos(646,68)\c&H091403&}KAMIO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:55.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:58.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl's in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't feeling very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:01.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so she's in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:02.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were there, she wouldn't rest up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're her mother, so it shouldn't bother her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:10.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm her mother, we do have other issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:20.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you aren't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:22.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:26.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I couldn't pick you up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:26.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:29.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're busy with other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:30.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:35.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like dinosaurs, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:39.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she like dinosaurs so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:40.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:43.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always liked them, ever since she was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:46.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't know anything about her, even though she's your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:51.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget that it was her birthday yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:56.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, does that girl act strangely during the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:58.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she always strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:59.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:02.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if there's nothing, then it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:08.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, enough with this trivial talk; it's finally the main event of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:13.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The erotic confessions corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:13.00,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,How did we get to that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:16.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just saying the title turns me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:17.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a pervert or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:19.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Romantic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:23.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because dinosaurs thrived for millions and millions of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:28.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but then they faced their end and went extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of sad and makes me emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:33.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still having those dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:35.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I still am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:39.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In my dreams, I'm going back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:41.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to describe it, but I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:48.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From the scent of the wind, the feel of the breeze on my skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:51.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the way the air moves, and the passing of the seasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:54.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I'm going back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:56.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of a dream like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:57.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:58.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:02.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where my dreams are taking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:07.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:07.16,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:08.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:08.17,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:09.35,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:11.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to get hit by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:10.12,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.01,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're cracking watermelons today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:11.91,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.04,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:15.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Kano wanted to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.21,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:15.44,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:17.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you spoiling her a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:17.08,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:18.42,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:21.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:22.49,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:34.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:36.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't make money here either...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:38.64,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:42.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:43.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't crash into me every time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:45.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you come yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:48.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:50.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:52.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't always act so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a little busy yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:17:00.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To make up for it, you will live here from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:00.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:00.86,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:02.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:05.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with, didn't you want me to leave town?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:08.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was different!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:15.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! He got up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:32.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't figure it out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:33.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:35.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is mysterious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:40.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have such a wonderful, special talent, Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:45.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Clap clap clap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:48.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can use a bit of what is called magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:50.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:54.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many mysteries in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:56.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I have a special thank-you gift.
