Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:57.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:11.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl with wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:13.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:16.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the same girl as my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:21.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:28.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a little girl, I had a picture book like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:29.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:35.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the picture book, there was a girl with pure white wings on her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:43.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a little girl, I dreamt of flying through the sky with her someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing strange about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:51.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even if the purpose of your journey is to look for her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:19:00.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because everyone has a destination they wish to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:08.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars are going to be beautiful again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:12.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:16.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it well at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:19.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming, Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:34.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A destination, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:12.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done with today's homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:28.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:28.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C-A-R-D-S.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:33.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:38.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to play cards with you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:42.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Play by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:46.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, we have come from a faraway planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:48.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:50.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:53.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:55.52,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:56.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:57.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:58.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano disappeared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:20:59.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:03.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already looked there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:05.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:07.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you two go that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:08.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san, do you have any idea where she might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:10.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:12.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to look anywhere we can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:20.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:22.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirishima-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:27.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:28.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:28.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:30.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pi-ka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:31.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pi-ka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:33.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he asking us to follow him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:36.39,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko piko piko piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:35.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The shrine again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:37.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she said she'd already looked there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:38.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:40.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:43.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tightly clasping my only treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:44.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:46.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:48.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:49.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:44.02,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fad(400,900)\fs51\shad2.25\pos(641,293)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:45.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-kun, I am writing this to you because I think you'll believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.71,0:23:50.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally decided to go to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.33,0:23:54.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling that it will make everyone happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.73,0:23:58.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling that I will meet the girl you are looking for too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:01.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how long it will take,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.58,0:24:04.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I will definitely bring her to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.83,0:24:09.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be grateful if you could help Onee-chan until I return.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.13,0:24:20.13,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,0)\fs39\fscx100\fscy100\shad2.4\c&HFEFEFA&\4c&H121213&\pos(954,417)}Episode 4
