Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.46,0:01:35.55,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}Chasing, chasing the fading vapor trails
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.42,0:01:43.20,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}It hasn't changed since the day we crossed that hill
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.46,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}And never will
